                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Hay</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Powell</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1904-02-16">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 16, 1904</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Hay acknowledges Mr. Powell’s telegram of the 9th instant, and states that
                    under custom prevailing in the Dominican Republic, military authorities are not
                    justified in invading consular offices and capturing refugees. Instructs him to
                    make proper representations.)</p>
            </div>
        </body>
